room_title: Escape room "The Book of Secrets" by The Puzzle Masters Escape Rooms in Tacoma
room_description: Rumors have swirled for decades about closely guarded government secrets. The rumors state there is a book that contains the answers to these conspiracies. Your team has been approached by an unknown group. They want you to infiltrate the President’s personal study, find and retrieve the Book of Government Secrets. The group’s “inside source” will get your team into the room. You will have 60 minutes to complete your mission. Can you succeed?
